events.text: The Timberwolves traded Jeff Teague to the Suns for Jevon Carter, Tyler Johnson, Jalen Lecque, Aron Baynes, and Cameron Johnson.
The Warriors traded D'Angelo Russell to the Timberwolves for Andrew Wiggins and a 2020 1st round pick (MIN).

The Mavericks traded Boban Marjanovic, Ryan Broekhoff, Antonius Cleveland, Courtney Lee, a 2020 2nd round pick (GSW), and a 2022 1st round pick (DAL) to the Lakers for Alex Caruso, Dwight Howard, Devontae Cacok, Kyle Kuzma, and Troy Daniels.
The Cavaliers traded Kevin Love to the Hornets for Michael Kidd-Gilchrist, Bismack Biyombo, P.J. Washington, and a 2020 1st round pick (CHA).
